<title>bnḥbk nsjd lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- bnḥbk nsjd lyk ạnt fạdynạ bnḥbk nrfʿ lyk kl ạ̉gẖạnynạ
 bnḥbk ạ̉nt lynạ kl mạ lynạ bnḥbk yạ ạlly sạkn fy ạ̉wạnynạ
 1- yạ sạkn jwh qlwbnạʿynynạ bttrjạk
 msẖ mmkn qlb hạysẖbʿ yạ yswʿ ạ̹lạ bmrậk
 sbb frḥ qlwbnạ ạ̹nnạ jnbyk
 wạlly yskn fy strk ylqy̱ ḥmạyth fyk
 2- qlbk mlyạn bạlrḥmẗ wạlkẖyr llmw̉mnyn
 wbtgẖmrnạ bạlnʿmẗ wbdmk mstwryn
 sbb rạḥẗ qlwbnạ ạnnạ fy ạ̹ydyk
 wạlly yậmn bṣlybk ylqy̱ ḍmạnh fyk</lyrics>
</song>